  "remarks": "National identification no.: Indonesian National Identity Card number 1127083101740003 under name Abdul Rosyid Ridho Ba’asyir. Father's name is Abu Bakar Ba'asyir (QI.B.217.06.). Brother of Abdul Rahim Ba’aysir (QI.B.293.11). Belongs to the leadership of and is involved in recruitment and fundraising for Jemmah Anshorut Tauhid (JAT) (QE.J.133.12.) Associated with Jemaah Islamiyah (QE.J.92.02.). Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 15 November 2021.; Listing: Listed by UN 1989 Committee on 12 March 2012.",
